Well I must admit…I may have been wrong about The Amazing Digital Circus. It’s been almost a YEAR since we’ve covered the series and everything I thought I knew has now been tuned upside down. In today’s episode, I’m going to be diving back in to see what’s gone right and how much I’ve actually gotten wrong…
